  "description": "Remove Bottom Border Radius from Gallery Item Images\n\nUpdate the CSS styling for images within gallery items to have square bottom corners instead of rounded ones.\n\nRequirements:\n- Target img elements that are children of .gallery-item containers\n- Remove or override border-radius on bottom-left and bottom-right corners\n- Preserve any existing top corner rounding if present\n- Ensure the change applies consistently across all gallery items\n- Verify visual appearance matches design intent (likely to align with a caption or container below the image)",
